CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1773159074
OL,3,CDonna Ockenden to chair Leeds
OL,4,Cmaternity investigation
OL,6,FThe independent investigation into
OL,7,Fmaternity and neonatal services at
OL,8,FLeeds Teaching Hospitals (LTH) NHS
OL,9,FTrust was ordered by Wes Streeting in
OL,10,FOctober.
OL,12,FAt the time, the Health Secretary said
OL,13,Fhe was "shocked" by "repeated
OL,14,Fmaternity failures" which were "made
OL,15,Fworse by the unacceptable response of
OL,16,Fthe trust".
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/14
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,363,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1773159074
OL,3,CDonna Ockenden to chair Leeds
OL,4,Cmaternity investigation
OL,6,FServices in Leeds were rated
OL,7,F"inadequate" in June last year
OL,8,Ffollowing an unannounced inspection
OL,9,Fprompted by concerns from families and
OL,10,Fwhistleblowers.
OL,12,FMs Ockenden's appointment comes after
OL,13,Fnumerous calls from grieving families
OL,14,Fthat she should head the
OL,15,Finvestigation, with concerns escalated
OL,16,Fto Prime Minister Sir Keir Starmer
OL,17,Flast month.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/14
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,363,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1773159074
OL,3,CDonna Ockenden to chair Leeds
OL,4,Cmaternity investigation
OL,6,FThe full terms of the Leeds
OL,7,Finvestigation have yet to be agreed,
OL,8,Fbut it is expected to look at events
OL,9,Fbetween 2011 and 2025.
OL,11,FCampaigning was led by Fiona Winser-
OL,12,FRamm and Daniel Ramm, Amarjit and
OL,13,FMandip Matharoo, and Lauren Caulfield,
OL,14,Fwhose babies all died at LTH.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/14
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,363,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1773159074
OL,3,CDonna Ockenden to chair Leeds
OL,4,Cmaternity investigation
OL,6,FResponding to Ms Ockenden's
OL,7,Fappointment, Ms Matharoo said: "It has
OL,8,Fbeen a long, drawn-out and emotionally
OL,9,Fdraining process to get the assurances
OL,10,Fthat this investigation will be
OL,11,Fhandled with the appropriate
OL,12,Fmethodology and care that it needs.
OL,14,F"We are grateful that Wes Streeting
OL,15,Fhas listened carefully to all of the
OL,16,Fevidence we put to him about our
OL,17,Fconcerns and why Donna should be
OL,18,Fappointed as chair.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/14
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,363,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1773159074
OL,3,CDonna Ockenden to chair Leeds
OL,4,Cmaternity investigation
OL,6,F"We believe she has the experience,
OL,7,Findependence and determination
OL,8,Frequired to uncover the truth and
OL,9,Fdeliver meaningful accountability and
OL,10,Fchange."
OL,12,FA statement from Ms Ockenden said: "It
OL,13,Fis an honour to have been asked to
OL,14,Fchair this review, and I feel a
OL,15,Fprofound sense of responsibility to
OL,16,Fthe parents, babies and healthcare
OL,17,Fprofessionals it concerns to ensure
OL,18,Fthat we get this right.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/14
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,363,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1773159074
OL,3,CDonna Ockenden to chair Leeds
OL,4,Cmaternity investigation
OL,6,F"This review must remain firmly
OL,7,Ffocused on the families who, in many
OL,8,Finstances, have waited far too long
OL,9,Ffor answers to questions about their
OL,10,Fcare.
OL,12,F"My priority will be to listen
OL,13,Fcarefully to families and staff, to
OL,14,Funderstand what has gone wrong, and to
OL,15,Fensure that the lessons are learned
OL,16,Fand the changes required are made, in
OL,17,Fa timely way, thus ensuring that all
OL,18,Fmothers, their babies and families
OL,19,Freceive safe, high-quality perinatal
OL,20,Fcare."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G7/14
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,363,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1773159074
OL,3,CDonna Ockenden to chair Leeds
OL,4,Cmaternity investigation
OL,6,FMs Caulfield said the appointment had
OL,7,Fcome 10 days before what would have
OL,8,Fbeen her daughter Grace's fourth
OL,9,Fbirthday.
OL,11,F"I feel this is the best gift I could
OL,12,Fgive her, ensuring her little life is
OL,13,Factually going to make a change," she
OL,14,Fsaid.
OL,16,F"We have fought for this review so
OL,17,Fthat families finally get answers and
OL,18,Fso that future parents in Leeds can
OL,19,Ffeel confident that both mothers and
OL,20,Fbabies will make it home safely."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G8/14
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,363,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1773159074
OL,3,CDonna Ockenden to chair Leeds
OL,4,Cmaternity investigation
OL,6,FMr Streeting spoke to families on
OL,7,FTuesday and the Government will start
OL,8,Fwork next month on setting out the
OL,9,Fterms of reference for the
OL,10,Finvestigation.
OL,12,FHe said: "To the families in Leeds, I
OL,13,Fwant to say thank you for your
OL,14,Fopenness during our detailed
OL,15,Fdiscussions in recent weeks, and the
OL,16,Fcourage you continue to show in
OL,17,Fsharing your experiences and
OL,18,Fadvocating for lasting change, so
OL,19,Fother families do not experience the
OL,20,Funimaginable tragedies you have gone
OL,21,Fthrough.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G9/14
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,363,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1773159074
OL,3,CDonna Ockenden to chair Leeds
OL,4,Cmaternity investigation
OL,6,F"This review must deliver for you and
OL,7,Ffor the sake of all families who
OL,8,Frightly expect to receive safe and
OL,9,Fhigh-quality maternity care in the NHS.
OL,11,F"Donna Ockenden's leadership will
OL,12,Fbring us closer to the lasting change
OL,13,Fso desperately needed in Leeds."
OL,15,FMs Ockenden has also reviewed mother
OL,16,Fand baby deaths at Shrewsbury and
OL,17,FTelford Hospital NHS Trust.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G10/14
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,363,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36211
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1773159074
OL,3,CDonna Ockenden to chair Leeds
OL,4,Cmaternity investigation
OL,6,FThere have also been calls for Ms
OL,7,FOckenden to lead an investigation into
OL,8,Fmaternity care at University Hospitals
OL,9,FSussex NHS Foundation Trust, which was
OL,10,Fannounced by Mr Streeting last June.
OL,12,FMs Winser-Ramm, whose daughter Aliona
OL,13,Fdied in 2020, said: "We are calling on
OL,14,Fall those who have been harmed, or
OL,15,Fwhose babies have been harmed, to
OL,16,Freach out and engage with the review.
OL,18,F"Whether it was 11 years ago or 11
OL,19,Fmonths ago, your experience matters.
OL,20,FYour baby's life and well-being
OL,21,Fmatters, as does yours."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G11/14
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,363,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36212
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1773159074
OL,3,CDonna Ockenden to chair Leeds
OL,4,Cmaternity investigation
OL,6,FMr Ramm also said the review should
OL,7,F"look closely at the role of
OL,8,Fregulators, including the Care Quality
OL,9,FCommission".
OL,11,FKatie Warner, a medical negligence
OL,12,Flawyer at Irwin Mitchell, which is
OL,13,Frepresenting more than 40 families
OL,14,Fimpacted by issues with maternity care
OL,15,Fin Leeds, said: "We have a significant
OL,16,Fnumber of ongoing maternity cases
OL,17,Fagainst Leeds Teaching Hospitals NHS
OL,18,FTrust and we continue to be approached
OL,19,Fon a regular basis.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G12/14
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,363,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36213
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1773159074
OL,3,CDonna Ockenden to chair Leeds
OL,4,Cmaternity investigation
OL,6,F"It's hugely encouraging that the
OL,7,Freview is beginning to move forward
OL,8,Fand all credit to the Leeds families
OL,9,Fand the support group for their hard
OL,10,Fwork and determination.
OL,12,F"It is important that terms of
OL,13,Freference are now finalised, with
OL,14,Finput from all parties, as soon as
OL,15,Fpossible so that the review can begin."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G13/14
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
